name: Muscle Workout
desciption: Regular strength training improves the health of your bones, muscles, and connective tissue. Building stronger muscles also raises your metabolic rate and helps you maintain a healthy weight.

name: pullups-gym-fitness
desciption: Just like any other muscle, your abs need a break too! That doesn't mean you can't activate your ab muscles during your warm-up with exercises like Planks, Inchworms, and other balance and stabilization exercises, but you shouldn't train them every day.
